makes me wanna puke.

00:32.391 --> 00:34.052
Oh, shit...

00:34.152 --> 00:36.254
Go back
to New York, Marcus.

00:36.354 --> 00:38.456
Stay far away
from all this.

00:38.556 --> 00:40.899
