I've been coming here?

00:42.640 --> 00:43.741
[Travis]:
Till we found her corpse,

00:43.841 --> 00:45.223
it was all ancient history.

00:45.323 --> 00:48.906
I want you to tell me
about Nola, who she was.

00:49.006 --> 00:50.387
I need to know
everything, Harry,

00:50.487 --> 00:52.349
